{"tid":2212612,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[六十幾歲點申請黎香港？]  有新來港人士到中銀分行取表格　申領1萬元津貼","createTime":"2020-09-22T03:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T05:19:36.000Z","uid":60281,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4f1bbdf59ee03bf31e1b62d8db4f2c8ef53cfd76","tid":2212612,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550941-20200922.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550941-20200922.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=2dcf10e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550941-20200922.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f963bcd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550941-20200922.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n今早9時許，在深水埗一間中國銀行有數名市民索取表格。<br />\n<br />\n現年67歲的蘇先生來港約4年，本身任職清潔工，自今年4月起失業，現時領取綜援，因此前來取申請表。家庭煮婦曹太太與丈夫來港均未足7年，她說任職保安的丈夫，月入僅1萬多元，相信兩人都符合資格申領。不過，她說申請表的字體細小，擔心未必懂得填寫，又說最快要等8星期才可領取津貼是有點遲，希望越早越好。<br />\n<br />\n有市民替來港1年多的妹妹索取表格，但不肯定妹妹是否符合申領資格。"},{"pid":"5a5b9b9951e853995d48c7f74738574c92fa9e1d","tid":2212612,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T03:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呃囇啲錢錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8796b04f943e824de4f